# Task Tracking

> Central task log for the agent team. Updated by PM and specialists.

## Task Status Legend
- 🟦 **PLANNED** - Defined, not started
- 🟨 **IN_PROGRESS** - Actively being worked on
- 🟩 **REVIEW** - Submitted, awaiting review
- ✅ **DONE** - Passed review, merged
- 🟥 **BLOCKED** - Waiting on dependency
- ⏭️ **SKIPPED** - Deferred/cancelled

